00:36:37.240 --> 00:36:47.830
Now, third, I’m listening to you, and you’re 
clearly a very confident storyteller,   

00:36:48.840 --> 00:36:52.880
and I often talk about the importance
 of all of us in Indonesia  

00:36:52.880 --> 00:36:55.670
being better storytellers.   

00:36:56.460 --> 00:36:59.300
-Oh yes, I remember 
 your lecture, Mr. Gita.   

00:36:59.300 --> 00:37:03.740
-In the international community 
 we’re not well known.   

