The ones more recognized are 
Indians as storytellers.   

00:37:09.520 --> 00:37:11.870
In Southeast Asia, maybe
 Singaporeans. 

00:37:14.230 --> 00:37:18.680
I think the positive attributes you have 
can really be spread more widely.  

00:37:18.900 --> 00:37:22.390
First, to help raise IQ.   

00:37:22.940 --> 00:37:26.110
Second, hopefully boost 
 our PISA score.   

00:37:26.600 --> 00:37:32.630
From 69th, maybe even to number one, 
or number five, or at least top 10.  

00:37:33.150 --> 00:37:38.640
 In Southeast Asia, only two countries 
are above the global average:   

00:37:38.640 --> 00:37:40.200
Singapore and Vietnam.   

00:37:40.480 --> 00:37:41.110
-Oh really?   

