– Because they can tell a story, and 
they’ve got the cognitive skills.

01:07:18.040 --> 01:07:21.860
- Smart people who can tell stories.  

01:07:21.860 --> 01:07:22.710
- Yes.

01:07:23.370 --> 01:07:26.840
– And if we had one or two CEOs 
in international companies, 

01:07:26.840 --> 01:07:28.840
that would boost Indonesia’s image 
and global trust.   

