People would start to think, “Turns out 
Indonesian talent is just as good.”   

01:07:32.420 --> 01:07:34.110
And that’s what we’re lacking.   

01:07:34.110 --> 01:07:38.200
That’s why I’m one of those who 
agree if someone’s already abroad,  

01:07:38.200 --> 01:07:43.640
"Fine, but prove yourself there. 
Build your career to the top.   

