01:16:57.440 --> 01:17:01.800
I see hope in this: A lot of people say,   

01:17:01.800 --> 01:17:06.040
“TikTok is disruptive, it’s ruining
 young people.”   

01:17:06.040 --> 01:17:10.560
But no, I still see hope. Why? 
I saw Dr. Felix, PhD,   

01:17:10.560 --> 01:17:14.970
educating people on TikTok for 7 minutes 
