01:17:16.010 --> 01:17:18.880
I made a 3-minute health video, 2 million views.     

01:17:18.880 --> 01:17:21.230
So there’s still hope. 
 -Yes. 

01:17:22.220 --> 01:17:29.130
Meaning we, who have large followings   

