and the intellectual ability to tell stories,

01:17:32.680 --> 01:17:36.570
Let’s start talking: 
Limit screen time to 3 hours.    

01:17:37.560 --> 01:17:43.080
And even if you hit 5 hours, 
make sure at least 30% of it 

01:17:43.080 --> 01:17:49.400
is not social media.  Zoom, Kindle,
 e-books, anything else.    

01:17:49.760 --> 01:17:56.590
If social media is your number one, 
your anxiety is going to get worse.    

01:17:56.800 --> 01:18:01.720
Now Gen X is different, Pak. Gen X is
 funny, they have low screen time,   

01:18:01.720 --> 01:18:05.690
but extremely high work stress.    

01:18:06.000 --> 01:18:11.210
Their stress levels are super high, 
and their stress release is either 

01:18:12.000 --> 01:18:14.760
super healthy or really unhealthy.   

01:18:14.760 --> 01:18:17.680
The healthy ones go running, 
do ultramarathons  

01:18:17.680 --> 01:18:20.944
Have you seen middle-aged men, 
55 years old, 

01:18:20.944 --> 01:18:24.760
suddenly hiking solo, biking for miles?

01:18:24.760 --> 01:18:26.490
During the pandemic, so many
 were cycling.   

01:18:26.490 --> 01:18:27.790
- I know a few.

01:18:27.790 --> 01:18:34.220
- Or playing futsal. So Gen X either releases 
stress in very healthy ways, or not at all.  

01:18:34.750 --> 01:18:39.630
Some eat lots of rich foods, they just love eating, 
what can you do? Some love traveling.    

01:18:39.840 --> 01:18:41.530
I only recently realized-

01:18:43.020 --> 01:18:45.320
I don’t know if any of your
 viewers are Gen X   

